articles.title: ‘The Boys’ Suffers Growing Pains in Its Darkest Season Yet: TV Review - Variety
articles.description: In its long-awaited Season 4, Amazon satire 'The Boys' shows some growing pains in its darkest season yet.
articles.content: You have to hand it to “The Boys.” Production on Season 4 of the Amazon action satire wrapped over a year ago, with its release delayed by subsequent strikes in the entertainment industry. (Season 3 … [+7106 chars]
